&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://web.archive.org/web/20141014190529/http://www.wilayat.net/index.php?option=com_content&amp;amp;view=article&amp;amp;id=3015:history-of-tabari-sahaba-are-killers-of-uthman&amp;amp;catid=197&amp;amp;lang=en#mozTocId100934&quot;&gt;Criticism by Mawla Ali (as) upon Uthman and his Governors&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
